   <p className="mt-4 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
     Active theme:{" "}
     <span className="font-medium text-foreground">
       {isDark ? "dark" : "light"}
     </span>
   </p>
   ```

### Step 9 — `apps/web/src/router.ts` (MODIFY)

Add `ThemeProvider` to the Wrap function, wrapping the existing providers:

```typescript
